quran[52]{c,v,t}:
  69,1,incontestable (event)
  69,2,Quod incontestable (event)
  69,3,It est enim incontestable
  69,4,Thamoud ‘Aad disbelieved Shocker
  69,5,Prout pro Thamoud they annihilated devastating quake
  69,6,Prout pro ‘Aad they annihilated persistent violent storm
  69,7,He unleashed it them 7 nox 8 feria violently Vos vide people tossed circiter like decayed palm trunks
  69,8,Vos invenit any trace de them
  69,9,(Pharaoh others eum sinners Sodom) est wicked
  69,10,They disobeyed messenger their Dominus. Consequently He requited them devastating requital
  69,11,flood devastating nos carried vos floating (ark)
  69,12,Nos rendered it lesson vos any listening ear understand
  69,13,When horn blown dodum
  69,14,Terra montis carried off crushed utterly crushed
  69,15,Est feria when inevitable event advenit pass
  69,16,Caelum crack fall apart
  69,17,angels est Tuus Dominus dominion tunc encompass 8 (universes)
  69,18,Ut feria vos exposed nihil de vos hidden
  69,19,Prout pro 1 qui receives his actum his rectus manus he dictus Advenit read my actum
  69,20,Ego perfecit believe ego habuit accountable
  69,21,He deserved happy vita
  69,22,In exalted Paradise
  69,23,Its fruits est intra reach
  69,24,Eat drink happily in return tuus works feria elapsus
  69,25,Prout pro eum dedit his actum his sinister manus he dictus Oh Ego wish ego nunquam received my actum
  69,26,Ego wish ego nunquam knew my account
  69,27,Ego wish my decessus est eternal
  69,28,My moneta non help me
  69,29,Totus my power est iit
  69,30,Take eum shackle eum
  69,31,Burn eum in Hell
  69,32,In chain est 70 arms long tie eum
  69,33,Pro he non believe in DEUS Major
  69,34,Nor perfecit he advocate feeding de poor
  69,35,Consequently he non habet friend hic
  69,36,Nor any food absque bitter variety
  69,37,Food pro sinners
  69,38,Ego juravit quod vos vide
  69,39,Ac quod vos non vide
  69,40,Hoc est utterance prenobilis messenger
  69,41,Non utterance poet; rarely perfecit vos believe
  69,42,Nor utterance soothsayer; rarely perfecit vos take heed
  69,43,revelation ex Dominus universe
  69,44,Habet he uttered any alius teachings
  69,45,Nos punished eum
  69,46,Nos stopped revelations eum
  69,47,Nullus de vos helped eum
  69,48,Hoc est reminder pro the righteous
  69,49,Nos know some de vos est rejectors
  69,50,It est sorrow disbelievers
  69,51,It est absolute truth
  69,52,Ergo vos glorify cognomen tuus Dominus Major